# FREDAsoft Cursor Rules

Follow `AGENTS.md` before implementing.
Consult `docs/ARCHITECTURE_DESIGN.md` for architecture/product decisions.
Consult `docs/ArchieHistory.md` when historical context is needed.
Never implement on `main`.
Investigate and report a plan before coding unless explicitly trivial.
Stop and ask if chat instructions conflict with `AGENTS.md` or protected areas are involved.
